name: Venice OG
description: Native to the free-wheeling California beach city it’s named after, Venice OG is a powerful sativa-dominant strain with energetic effects that make it great for daytime use. Almost devoid of any sleepy effects, Venice will have you ready to work on projects, run errands or just hang out on the beach.
attributes_title: Happy, Uplifted, Creative, Relaxed, Tingly, Stress, Depression, Pain, Fatigue, Headaches, Dry Eyes, Headache, Dry Mouth, Paranoid
